Description: Smart imaging service enabling on-demand crop image manipluation.
 thumbor is a smart imaging service. It enables on-demand crop, resizing and
 flipping of images.
 .
 It also features a VERY smart detection of important points in the image for
 better cropping and resizing, using state-of-the-art face and feature detection
 algorithms.
